<h1>My favourite DIYs</h1>
    <h2>Natural LIP SCRUB</h2>
    
    <p>I will explain how to make your own homemade lip scrub with really simple things that everybdy has at home</p>
    <p>Ingredients:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Small container</li>
        <li>Brown sugar</li>
        <li>Olive oil</li>
        <li>Pink sweet drink</li>
    </ul>
<ol>
    <li>Get a small container where you want to place your lip scrub."You can find this in a dollar store"</li>
    <li>Fill the container with brown sugar almost until the edge.</li>
    <li>Now, pour the olive oil into the sugar until the sugar is perfectly convert and it absorbs the oil.</li>
    <li>For a pink lip scrub, add some pink sweet drink like granadine to oi.</li>
    <li>Enjoy your soft lips!</li>
    </ol>
